title: Sichuan-Glazed Salmon with Creamy Slaw & Rice Pre-Prepped | Three Steps | Ready in 15
description: With pre-chopped, pre-marinated ingredients, our new Fresh & Fast recipes are on the table in just 15 minutes. Perfect for busy weeknights - and busy people. This week, enjoy salmon with a mouth-watering Sichuan garlic glaze and a crisp and creamy slaw.

*Heads-up - you'll need a microwave for this recipe.*
